name: Pannai Sivam Fruits
description: trading and supplying fresh fruits and v
overview:
Pannai Sivam Fruits established in 1996 is an well-known firms in the industry, engaged in wholesaling, trading, supplying an extensive array of Fresh Fruits, Tropical Fruits, Fresh Bananas, Green Vegetables, Fresh Vegetables, Fresh Potatoes and Sweet Corns.

Our Products: Green Vegetables, Fresh Vegetables, Fresh Potatoes,Sweet Corns

Our Quality: Our trustworthiness lies in offering quality assured array of products to our clients. To maintain the same, we have developed sophisticated quality testing department which is operated by our skilled quality controllers who examine the entire product range in different parameters.

Vendor Base: Our entire product range is sourced from trustworthy and authorized vendors of the industry, who are selected by our procurement agents after conducting the rigorous research. They are selected on the basis of financial stability, quality, and trust and prompt delivery schedules.

Our Clients: Clients are considered as the valuable asset of our clients. We leave no stone unturned in satisfying the diverse requirements of the clients. We offer customization packaging solutions of the entire product range which are as per the exact requirements of our clients. Our strict pursuit towards quality standards has assisted us to mark remarkable position in the competitive industry.
